Mail/ISO2022JP version 0.06 (Final)
===========================

 This module composes a ISO-2022-JP encoded email.

**DEPRECATED**

 This module has moved to the namespace of Lingua::JA::Mail.
 So this module will be no more maintenanced.
 Please see its successor Lingua::JA::Mail.

INSTALLATION

 To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

 This module requires perl5.8 or later.

 This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Encode
   MIME::Base64

